SEARCH
Module dev.riko.golftourplanner
Package dev.riko.golftourplanner.pathfinding

Class SearchOptimalTrip

java.lang.Object
dev.riko.golftourplanner.pathfinding.SearchOptimalTrip
public class SearchOptimalTrip extends Object
This class represents a search for the optimal trip between two places in a world map, using Dijkstra's algorithm to find the shortest path between the places.
